OL,5,G0600 Teleshopping
OL,6,G0700 Shop: Thane Offers
OL,7,     FVisit Thane.tv and browse our
OL,8,     Fselection of award winning home
OL,9,     Fand fitness products that let you
OL,10,     Fdo more with less!
OL,11,G0800 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,12,     FWe meet Tracey and Mike, who run
OL,13,     Ftwo bars on the Costa Del Sol. The
OL,14,     Ffirst was bought from its original
OL,15,     Fowner on an especially good night
OL,16,     Fduring a holiday four years ago!
OL,17,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,18,     FMeet Joe and Jan, a couple of
OL,19,     Fwell-loved characters who have
OL,20,     Fbeen married for 49 years and will
OL,21,     Fbe familiar to fans.
