OL,5,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,6,     FKate's tenants are suing her for
OL,7,     Ftrying to evict them. After a
OL,8,     Fhealth scare, Tim wants to sell
OL,9,     Fhis property, but his tenant
OL,10,     Frefuses to leave.
OL,11,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,12,     FThere's a four car collision
OL,13,     Foutside a primary school, and a
OL,14,     Fspeeding driver, desperate to
OL,15,     Fescape, smashes into traffic at a
OL,16,     Fjunction, causing carnage before
OL,17,     Fescaping on foot.
