OL,5,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FThe healthcare professionals and
OL,7,     Fstaff at the Hall Green Health
OL,8,     FCentre have 26,000 patients on
OL,9,     Ftheir books, with problems ranging
OL,10,     Ffrom sore feet to self-harm.
OL,11,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,12,     FBarnsley's A&E department is put
OL,13,     Funder the microscope. There are
OL,14,     Fcomplications when Wendy, who
OL,15,     Fsuffers from kidney failure, is
OL,16,     Fadmitted with a heart condition.
